graph TD
    Start((Start)) --> Init[Initialize Project<br/>npm/uv init]
    Init --> Deps[Install SDKs<br/>@modelcontextprotocol/sdk]
    
    subgraph Core Logic
    Deps --> DefineTools[Define Tools<br/>JSON Schema + Logic]
    DefineTools --> DefineResources[Define Resources<br/>Read-only Data]
    end
    
    DefineResources --> ServerInit[Initialize MCP Server Instance]
    ServerInit --> Transport[Choose Transport Layer<br/>Stdio or HTTP/SSE]
    ServerInit --> ClientInit[Initialize MCP Client<br/>Connect to Server]
    serverInit --> Register[Register Tools & Resources<br/>with MCP Server]
    
    
    subgraph Testing
    Transport --> Inspector[Run MCP Inspector]
    Inspector --> Debug{Works?}
    Debug -- No --> DefineTools
    end

    
    Debug -- Yes --> Config[Add to Client Config<br/>claude_desktop_config.json]
    Config --> End((Deploy & Use))


    style Start fill:#f9f,stroke:#333
    style End fill:#bbf,stroke:#333
    style Debug fill:#fff4dd,stroke:#d4a017